 "awd_abstract_narration": "Studies in theoretical physics will focus on                               investigations of geometric phases in quantum mechanics which                   are generalizations of those originally discovered by Berry,                    and on quantum mechanical phase shifts which can occur in the                   presence of electromagnetic or gravitational potentials.  These                 investigations concern the fundamental character of quantum                     mechanics, and will help to illuminate the subtle nature of                     this theoretical framework in terms of which essentially all                    submicroscopic physical phenomena are understood.",
